{"tid":991100,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"全球用家悲歌！M$ 正式放棄Windows 10 Mobile，12月後開始全面停止更新！！","createTime":"2019-01-22T06:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T08:26:47.000Z","uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7002b1af6f74f1cdee0866f83e8967e763f05a45","tid":991100,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:29:17.000Z","msg":"微軟將在今年12月10日全面終止更新Windows 10 Mobile，同時也準備終止釋出安全漏洞修補檔案。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/01/20/draft/5821166.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F01%2F20%2Fdraft%2F5821166.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=482b752d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n在原本規劃中，微軟預期藉由Windows 10跨裝置使用特性，期望將行動裝置整合進Windows 10平台市場，但無奈與iOS、Android平台市場競爭失利，加上Windows 10 Mobile的使用體驗始終不佳，因此讓微軟在後續間接捨棄發展Windows 10 Mobile，轉而利用iOS、Android平台發展自有服務，因此也註定Windows 10 Mobile裝置步入發展末路的命運。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/amp/story/11017/3604126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fstory%2F11017%2F3604126&d=eHGin6srybVV6v6u95%2FlF0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=46343175\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/amp/story/11017/3604126</a>"},{"pid":"e578a54ff8a33c9040a97018bddc09b3fc266c19","tid":991100,"uid":20914,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:32:52.000Z","msg":"想知直至現時為止重有幾多人用"},{"pid":"0cf92e270e77ce0c503274336893a36491a2dce1","tid":991100,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:47:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c633be9fca219d5e3e496559189d2887b4c05be2","tid":991100,"uid":26650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:55:12.000Z","msg":"6.5 -&gt; 7 -&gt; 8.1 -&gt; 10<br />\n連斬3 次，app唔